": 375}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Crowd trouble forcedthe first football match of Paris 2024to be suspended for nearly two hours, as Morocco fansinvaded the pitch and threw objects at Argentina players.\", \"from\": 380, \"to\": 548, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 428, \"end\": 433, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.99999999979741, \"rank\": 2.0255230909335426e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 479, \"end\": 486, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999998633484, \"rank\": 1.334452403568383e-10, \"text\": \"Morocco\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 530, \"end\": 539, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999479166504, \"rank\": 5.206341178987988e-08, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Crowd\", \"from\": 380, \"to\": 385}, {\"ngram\": \"trouble\", \"from\": 386, \"to\": 393}, {\"ngram\": \"forcedthe first football match\", \"from\": 394, \"to\": 424}, {\"ngram\": \"nearly two hours\", \"from\": 458, \"to\": 474}, {\"ngram\": \"the pitch\", \"from\": 499, \"to\": 508}, {\"ngram\": \"objects\", \"from\": 519, \"to\": 526}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The violence came after Argentina looked to have scored an equaliser in the 16th minute of stoppage time and prompted the referee to order both teams into the changing rooms.\", \"from\": 550, \"to\": 724, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 574, \"end\": 583, \"title\":