"from\": 1216, \"to\": 1226}, {\"ngram\": \"the chaotic ending\", \"from\": 1249, \"to\": 1267}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This would not even happen in a neighbourhood tournament.\", \"from\": 1269, \"to\": 1327, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a neighbourhood tournament\", \"from\": 1300, \"to\": 1326}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's pathetic.\", \"from\": 1328, \"to\": 1342, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Beyond the Olympic spirit, the organisation needs to be up to standard and, at the moment, unfortunately, it is not.\", \"from\": 1344, \"to\": 1460, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic spirit\", \"from\": 1351, \"to\": 1369}, {\"ngram\": \"the organisation\", \"from\": 1371, \"to\": 1387}, {\"ngram\": \"standard\", \"from\": 1406, \"to\": 1414}, {\"ngram\": \"the moment\", \"from\": 1423, \"to\": 1433}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have not been a coach for long, but never in my career as a player have I seen a situation like that.\", \"from\": 1461, \"to\": 1564, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a coach\", \"from\": 1477, \"to\": 1484}, {\"ngram\": \"my career\", \"from\": 1508, \"to\": 1517}, {\"ngram\": \"a player\", \"from\": 1521, \"to\": 1529}, {\"ngram\": \"a situation\", \"from\": 1542, \"to\": 1553}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is a circus.\\\"\", \"from\": 1565, \"to\": 1581, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a circus\", \"from\": 1571, \"to\": 1579}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The former Liverpool and West Ham midfielder added: \\\"I told the boys that now we need to look forward, try to get the six points that will allow us to qualify and that all this should fill us with energy and anger for what we have ahead of us.\\\"\", \"from\": 1583, \"to\": 1828, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1594, \"end\": 1603, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.582815289120663e-16, \"text\": \"Liverpool\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q242